communal-catharsis-p: Communal catharsis is - quite simply - catharsis reached through community. It's finding a new peace, a new clarity, or a new inspiration by sharing and processing your life with others and learning about life through other people's experiences. Together we are creating a journal for the collective conciousness.
processing-the-present-p: As humans we have a need to process and understand our world and our existence. Journaling is an easy and effective way to process your day to day. By doing it so in community, you also have the words and support of others to help you navigate.
quote: You don't need any writing experience. It's like sitting around the fire and sharing stories with people, but in an App.
sharing-and-caring-p: Express your honest thoughts, feelings, and stories in a safe space, with a community that appreciates authenticity and celebrates vulnerability.
express-yourself-p: Journaling is a simple and powerful way to understand ourselves and the world around us. By journaling in a community, you can benefit from the wisdom and encouragement of others who are also exploring their thoughts and experiences. Together, we can create a collective journal and help each other navigate life's journey.
connect-with-a-community-p: Share your thoughts, feelings, and experiences with our supportive community that values honesty and vulnerability. You don't need writing experience - just be yourself! If you need ideas, try our writing prompts or get inspired by reading other peopleâ€™s journal entries.
sharing-is-caring-p: Experience a space free from judgment and competition. Our guidelines ensure online safety so you can comfortably share your thoughts and feelings. Connect with others by joining interest-based groups. Read stories, and engage in meaningful conversations. Discover a newfound understanding by sharing your stories and learning from others' experiences.
hear-from-our-founder: Hear from our founder, Ivana de Maria, on how Storyplace plays a role in our society.

storyplace-is-a-socual-journaling: Storyplace is the first social journaling app, where people from around the world share their journal entries, stories, feelings, and thoughts in a supportive community.
a-modern-day-virtual-virtual-bonfire: Our platform helps you develop a healthy journaling habit with prompts, topics and writing challenges, while fostering meaningful connections with others.
our-community-platform-focuses: We prioritize mental health and well-being by removing harmful features found in traditional social media and creating a safe space for authentic self-expression.
our-purpose: Our purpose is to help you nurture personal growth and build a community.
